author: @ТатьянаЛеонова-ю5ж
text:
Это красивый корейский паренёк или мужчина в какой-то степени продукт своей страны и прекрасной работы стилистов. Там много таких красавцев-"корейских мальчиков.". Не знаю как этот, а многие ещё и поют замечательно. Очень люблю корейские дорамы. Они непрттязательные, но какие-то чистые, позитивные, юморные. Классные. А время любого такого человека на помостксх очень бвстротечно. Пусть покрасуется, пока можно и позволено ему временем. Что мне в России до его интеллекта, как начала придираться одна дама. Ей то что с того? Она что общаться с ним собирается? Вообще корейцы стараются детям давать нормальное образование, а к выпускному иногда делают им подарок-посещение классного косметолога для "исправления недостатков  лица. Хотя какие здесь недостатки и с такой грацией. Молодость. Следит за собой. Уважает и любит себя в хорошем нужном смысле слова. Не буду сравнивать наших парней. Этот умеет поднести и держать себя. И не опустится до жуткой разрисовки своей молодой кожи, уродующей на всю жизнь и не воткнет в нос, язык, ухо  гадость, чтобы показаться в тренде(це). Модно было, есть и будет Естественная красота и привлекательность, если только что-то подштриховать. Но без уродства-лиловые пряди, зелёная щетина, проткнутые брови.
Любуюсь этим корейцем.!

author: @vetcheagle
text:
You're going crazy, aren't you, Bang Sihyuk? You're about to lose your mind, aren't you, Bang Sihyuk? Isn't Jimin a legendary MMA performance? With his legendary beauty, legendary voice, legendary dance and legendary talent, he captivated everyone and all the audience. You're about to lose your mind with your bad ambition, aren't you, Bang Sihyuk? Whatever you do, stepmother Cinderella is always the princess. Whatever you do, stepmother Bang Sihyuk, two ugly girls will never succeed in than Cinderella, right?
"You're closing all my mail accounts. It does not matter to me. You're not a god. Yeah, you think you're a god, Bang Sihyuk, but you're not a god. I'm not Korean either. I'm not going to shake my head at you like a water pumpkin and lm going to share your wrong moves. It's okay for me to get new mail. I don't insult you. I'm just doing character analysis. We live in a free world. You can't stop my freedom of thought."
" A special letter to Bts boss Bang Sihyuk:
I'm a psychologist and an analyst. My life is spent analyzing the human character. That's how I make money. In my personal life I am also a fan of BTS and Jimin. l love Bts and Park Jimin. My bias is jimin but l'm realist and objective because l'm psicologist. Mr. Bang Sihyuk, I have decided to write this letter for your analysis. I hope you reach awareness and turn the right way. I hope you read this.I kept asking why you don't like Jimin. Why don't you like Jimin? Why are you torturing her? Why are you keeping him in the background? I kept asking these questions. And from the past I started to analyze you because I was curious about the answers to these questions. I know now I hope you understand. You're an ambitious man. You are very ambitious. You think you're very smart. You always think you're making the right decisions. That's how you think you're so successful. But you know you've made a big mistake, and you can't accept it. When setting up the Bts group, you made selections and selected jk and v as the star. You have designated other members as complementary members to support them. You didn't notice Jimin's unique abilities. You didn't realize what a talented and industrious sun Jimin was. You realized these abilities and the light too late. But you're an arrogant person. You couldn't admit you made a mistake. It was impossible for you to admit that you chose the wrong people as stars. As a result, you constantly advertising jk and v, you spent a lot of money for jk and v , you gave American trainings, you had aesthetics. But it didn't work, did it? None of the bad stuff you did to Jimin, did it? The sun and angelic light in his jimin has always won. He has always won unique abilities. Please accept that you've made a mistake now. Start walking the right way. Don't torture Jimin any more. Don't be more arrogant. You're a human being, you can make a mistake. Now give your Jimin the rightful victory. Let him use his abilities. Consider Jimin as the sun. Please don't fight anymore. Peace with him and especially with yourself. You make big ads for the wrong people. You spend big money on the wrong people. Please walk the right way now.You didn't make them. You're not a god. They were already very talented people. You can't give up the people you think you're creating, and you want the members to stay where you want them. This is not justice. We're army. We're not gonna let that happen. We will always do justice. We're millions. Let Jimin rise like the sun, please."

author: @jj.bbangtann5643
text:
Dear jin, 
I wanna start off by saying happy birthday!! I hope u had a great day! Have you eaten yet? Remember to sleep and eat well💜 i just want to say thank you for everything u and bts has done for me in these past few months. Before i knew you guys, i was well depressed and had a lot of anxiety about schools and etc(i wont get into the details)  but anyways i just wanted to say a few words. I want to thank you for helping me get back on track with my life. The first song that i looked into was epiphany. I read the lyrics, listen closely to the tone, and i started feeling like i was not alone for once. It was hard for me to open up because i was scared. Now, im still pretty scared but i have improved just a little bit. I started to listen to all of bts's songs and realized that these lyrics arent JUST lyrics, they are something else. Something wonderful... something incredible. It was very hard to love myself. I looked in the mirror, and always hated what i saw. I started to compare myself to others. I started to cover myself up...hiding myself from the world. But you, you and bts, changed all that. Now i am no longer like that, although i get sad then and there, it does not affect me that much anymore. Your music helped me focus more on school and now instead of c's d's and f's, i got straight A's. I love you so much! I appriciate what u and what the rest of bts does to help others through music. I know it can be very tiring, but i know you can do it. I believe in you. You are KIM SEOKJIN after all. You are a part of BTS (The Most incredible, amazing, unpredicable, wonderful...ok sorry thats for another time heh) but what i was trying to say is, you are an incredible person. You just dont know how you and the rest of bangtan impacted my life. I will always be here to support you. If you feel like you are about to give up, look back at what you have done. Look at how much armys love you. You and bangtan deserves so much more love. Thank you so much for everything. I know that you dont know me but i know that you are here with me through your music. Thank you again. I love you. Dont forget to sleep and eat well, dont be too hard on yourself,and remember that bts and TRUE armys are right by your side. I have much more to say but thats for another time. I love you and have a wonderful birthday.

-your dearest fan, JD💜💜💜

author: @jackybaduria806
text:
*:¨·.·¨:*
*`·.To: Jin ♡*
    *From: Jacky ♡*

Dear Jin,
Happy birthday🥰🥳🎉✨ I remember last year! It was the most memorable birthday to me especially since it was the first time I got to spend mine with yours! I hope this day will feel really special to you spent with the members and also with ARMY. Sharing the same birthday with you makes this day feel even more special to me especially since I get to celebrate it with someone whom I love very much, along with my twin sister💜 Thank you for being an amazing hyung in the group of BTS. It wouldn’t be the same without you. Thank you for being the mood maker of the group, and for always giving us a laugh. It’s amazing how contagious your smile and laugh is. I really hope that those won’t ever fade away from your face. I hope you know that ARMYs love you so much and are so proud of how far you have come! Life is hard, but don’t ever give up! ARMYs will always have your back, we promise😊

To the amazing hyung, Jin, I just want to say that you are doing amazing! You have worked so hard to get to where you are now and we ARMYs couldn’t be any prouder of you. A lot of things have been going through your head during your past days; during your pre-debut days. Your mom would just watch and listen to her friends bragging about their sons. You wanted to be a son that not only your mom could be proud of, but also both your parents could be proud of. Something was always off with you. Something strange. Something you were always confused and worried about. You wanted to become a lawyer just like your father, but soon realized you wanted to become an actor after getting inspired by someone by watching a drama. After you got casted on the streets by BigHit, you auditioned to become an actor like you always wanted to be, but when BigHit had other plans for you, that became hard for you.

These days, I keep thinking about it. You were just casted for your good looks; for your visuals. After singing in front of BigHit, it may have not sounded all great. I understand that. You didn’t have any experience in singing at all and never thought you’d want to do singing as a career. This was the hardest moment for you. It’s as if all the darkness had gone inside your body. You didn’t know if taking this path of becoming a K-Pop idol and a vocalist of the very first boy group of BigHit was right. It just didn’t feel right to you. It’s unusual how you took a path towards something you never had passion in. But you know, you never gave up and kept going. Where would this path take you? Somewhere beautiful or somewhere awful? Of course, you didn’t have any expectations. You just had to walk through life you know.

At the beginning of your career, you had a lot of worries, but you worked hard no matter how hard it was. Although you must have had a lot of struggles, you continued to do the best you could. You practiced continuously on your vocals and dancing. Maybe you cried because you couldn’t sing nor dance. Maybe you cried because it was a struggle for you. But you knew one thing. There is no success without struggles. So you worked your butt off all day and night to improve on everything. You wanted to make your parents proud. Maybe even hoping one day your mom could brag about you to her friends. Well, you did it! I am so proud of you😭

국제 아미가 당신에게 편지를 쓰고 있습니다. 비록 아미 출신이었던 모든 세월 동안 귀하의 문화에 대해 충분히 알고 있지만, 나는 언어를 모르기 때문에 오해 할 수 있습니다.  나는 내가 실패하고 완전히 잘못된 것을 쓸 수 있다고 정말로 걱정한다.

당신의 눈이이 편지를 읽지 않더라도, 나는 당신이 매우 강하고 용감하고 인내하는 사람이라고 말하고 싶습니다. 당신의 일에 대한 열정은 감탄할 가치가 있습니다. 실제로, 나는 당신이 된 사람을 자랑스럽게 생각합니다.  내가 어제 진이를 사랑했듯이, 나는 지금 진이를 사랑하고, 내일의 진이도 사랑할 것입니다. 왜냐하면 당신을 모르더라도, 나는 당신이 매우 특별하고 재미 있고 겸손한 사람이라는 것을 알고 있습니다.  절대 변경하지 마십시오.

그러나 혼동하지 마십시오. 낭만적 인 사랑이 아니며, 당신에 대한 나의 사랑은 무조건적입니다. 당신은 그것이 팬 대 아이돌 사랑이라고 말할 수 있습니다. 그러나 그것은 나를 위해 그 이상입니다. 무대 위에서 빛을 발하며 내 아름다움과 재능으로 마음을 녹인 석진과 비디오 게임을 즐기고 음식을 즐기는 것을 좋아하는 석진은 바람막이 유리 와이퍼 웃음으로 하루를 밝게 비춘다. 우리는 당신이있는 그대로 당신을 사랑하므로 절대로 자신을 의심하지 마십시오.

나는 당신이 당신의 생일을 많이 즐기기를 바랍니다. 나는 수업 중에 뷔라이브를 보았 음을 고백합니다. 아미가 아닌 친구조차도 당신이 매우 잘 생겼고 귀엽다고 말했지만 내 인터넷은 갔고 계속 볼 수 없었습니다. 그 순간이 나를 매우 행복하게 해주었 고, 나는 그 행복을 당신에게 돌려주기 위해 최선을 다했지만 결코 충분하지 않을 것이라고 생각합니다.

나는 당신을 사랑하고 당신이 훌륭하다고 말하 을 것입니다.

어쨌든, 나는 당신에게 말할 것이 많지만 할 수 없습니다. 내가 항상 당신의 날개가 될 것임을 잊지 십시오. 내가 또한 가장 필요할 때 당신을 위해 거기에있을 것입니다.

제가 한국어 를 잘 못해서 우리 석진 이 에게 미안 하지만 제가 많이 사랑 해요 😔💜

author: @nathufo
text: So adorable. I waited until midnight in my country to wish you a happy 27th birthday. I'm not Korean so for me you are 27. I don't want to hear you saying again you are old. but I suppose you won't care 🤭 even if you feel that way because part of your Armys are just babies. Time flies so fast so enjoy each moment. I wanted to say that you sing beautifully. I was so happy to hear you sing live. I hope I will get to see the group perform again. You are the perfect hyung for bangtan. You always create a fun mood that put everyone at ease. You support them so well and they seem so happy around you. Armys love you. Even your savage quotes on weverse make the fandom laugh for days. I got a big smile on my face while writing these lines. Thank you for being you. I wish you many happiness. Please stay healthy and don't forget to keep time for yourself. Lots of love and happy birthday again.

author: @cmoreira2005
text:
진, 오늘은 정말 특별한 날입니다. 전과 같이 BTS와 함께 마지막 생일을 즐기시기 바랍니다. 당신은 내가 당신을 사랑하는 색과 소테를 너무 잘 알고 있으며, 당신없이 내가 지나가는 세월은 항상 나와 함께있는 것처럼 알게 될 것입니다. 이 세상을 그리워하는 사람은 누구보다 많이 알고 있습니다 .. 솔직히 인생이주는 것에 행복하기를 바랍니다. 이 날은 완벽 할 것입니다 (아마도 나머지 멤버들을 망쳐 놓을 것이지만, 그것은 당신의 하루를 완벽하게 만듭니다).
나는 정말로 큰 여행을하는 것을 좋아합니다. 이것이 얼마나 큰지 신경 쓰지 않기를 바랍니다. 우주에서 가장 행복한 사람이 되세요. 오늘 당신을 막을 수있는 것은 없었습니다. 나는 그곳에 있고 싶었지만 여전히 나는 그곳에 있다는 것을 알고 있습니다. . 당신은 모든 ARMYS가이 날을 응원하고 하루를 하루로 만듭니다. 운이 좋으시면 BTS 멤버가 옆에 있고 내 마음이 많이 남아 있습니다. 어깨가 슬프다면 BTS가 있고 행복하면 BTS가 행복과 승리를 나눕니다.
아아! 나는 정말로 당신을 행복하게보고 싶습니다. 그리고 나는 2 년간의 ARMY에서 당신을 볼 수있었습니다. 비밀을 알고 싶니? 그러나 당신은 아무에게도 말하지 않으며 BTS 만 알 수 있습니다.평생 BTS가 정복 한 것처럼 아무도 내 마음을 정복 한 적이 없으며 결코 당신처럼 정복하지 않을 것입니다. 당신은 내 인생의 첫 번째 진정한 사랑입니다. 그리고 하나 더 비밀. 나는 당신과 당신의 재능을 미치게 사랑합니다. 진, 나는이 멋진 날을 당신과 함께 떠난다. 오늘의 조언 : 내일은 아무것도 같지 않기 때문에 오늘 당신의 소원 중 일부를 실현하십시오.
음! 이것은 나의 모든 자부심, 사랑, 애정, 그리고 온 마음을 가진 나의 여정이었다 말해
"마지막 때까지 내 맘을 지켜 줄게"❤❤❤❤❤❤❤🔥
🔥❤BTS_ARMY_FOREVER❤🔥

text:
!!!! HAPPY BIRTHDAY!!!!  ❤❤❤


그 모든 것이이 "아기"의 삶에서 잘 돌아가고 있으며 그는 자신보다 훨씬 더 가치가 있습니다. 그러나 그가 행복하다면 누구를 판단 할 수 있습니까? .. RJ 축하합니다. 진을 너무 사랑합니다. 그 이유 중 하나는 여러분 모두가 저를 사랑하도록 도와 주었기 때문입니다. BTS와 Kpop은 잊을 수없는 전설이며 군대가 사실이 될 것입니다. 그러나 당신과 다른 사람들이 행복하다면, 기뻐합니다. 당신이 군대에 혼자 가면 진 .. 내가 여기에 있고 싶은 이유는 우리를 지원하고 우리가 일어나서 다시 쓰러지지 않도록 도와주는 당신이기 때문에 가능한 한 빨리 돌아 오십시오. 그러나 나는 당신의 행복에 행복합니다. 각각의 미소는 싸움을하고 결코 포기하기에 충분합니다. 언젠가 나는 쇼에 가고, 정직한 .. 나는 당신의 모든 미소를 사랑하지만 세상에 순식간에 행복을 끝내는 나쁜 사람들이 있다는 것을 아는 것은 아프다! 진이이 글을 읽고 있다면 .. "나의 사랑", 나는 당신을보고 무엇이든 할 것입니다. 나는 많은 행복을 울었습니다. 아마 언젠가 .. 너희들은 내 도시에서 공연을 할 수 있니? (마리카)  그렇다면 ... 도착을 기다리고 있습니다. 그러나 그렇지 않다면, 나는 당신의 인생이 바쁘다는 것을 이해합니다 .. Jin / RJ 나는 당신을 너무 사랑하고 당신의 인생이 길고 희망이 있기를 바랍니다, 나는 당신을 너무 사랑합니다 .. RJ ❤❤❤

author: @yoongisbitch2579
text:
Happy birthday to the Mr.World Wide Handsome. We, ARMY, appreciate how much you have contributed to BTS. Thank you for being strong for us through the tough times. Apologies for the times that you have felt left out or less than what you are at times. We want you to know you are so special. Bangtan Sonyedan is never complete without you! Your hard work as the eldest and watching out for the others pays off seeing you raised proper children lol. But really, just know, despite all the hate you may get from many that our love for you is much bigger. We care for you, cheer for you, and want--from time to time-- to be a shoulder you can lay on in times of distress and relax. You've done plenty--- more than we can ever bargain for by removing our pain and stresses through your overwhelming lovely heart, jokes, and bright behaviour. We truly love you. Forever and always and we want you to know there is nobody like you that could take your place in our hearts. 
       With Love,
                        ARMY~💖

P.S: Everytime you blow kisses, my wig gets snatched. You must warn furst as a precaution.

author: @jesuscristo2231
text:
[#HappyJinDay] Happy birthday Jin!
 I remember exactly the day I met you.  I remember his smile, his shyness, and his drawn eyes that smiled overflowing with happiness.  I barely knew then that I was about to meet someone so wonderful that it would change my life in some way.

 I didn't know your name, but I knew you were different, your eyes told me that.  You looked at the camera and showed such shyness, but over time that was changing.  You have grown, matured, become a man.  Strong, kind, zealous and friend.  Someone who has inspired me every day, someone who has filled a great void in me, and taught me never to give up, to persist voraciously in my dreams, for there is no big enough barrier that I cannot break.  Just as you did and have been doing.

 All of us (your true fans) have seen your efforts and your results.  Your vocal, your acting, your limb care, your dancing.  Yes, SeokJin!  Your dance!  Each year it becomes more noticeable that you have been trying your best - and beyond - to improve, but even if you can't do it all perfectly, the way you would like it, it doesn't matter!  Do you know why?  Because you are so much more than that.  Because your true achievement is your effort, your determination, your perseverance.  This is what makes you special, what makes you different.  It is your immense ability to love something so much that you can do nothing less than your best.  Even if it costs you a lot.

 How my heart hurts that on this special day I cannot be with you, give you a hug, thank you;  look into your eyes and tell you all that you mean to me.  But despite the distance, I hope you can feel all the good energies I send you.  All my affection, gratitude and, especially, all my love for you.

 Thank you for providing me with wonderful experiences and sharing your life with all of us.  I am grateful for your teaching, for all that has put me through.  Thank you for yesterday, where happiness was present.  I appreciate the night of rest, where sweet dreams reigned.  And it all just happened thanks to you.  Thank you for your words that brought me strength, peace, joy and happiness.  Strength to fight and overcome difficulties.  Joy for the simple pleasure of living.  Peace because you calmed my heart.  Happiness because only those who love are happy, and you have taught me to love again.

 May you be happy today and every other day of your life.  May your happiness only increase, more and more, and may the love of all the people who love you - truly - accompany this growth.

 Through this message, I want to thank you and congratulate you.  I want you to know everything you mean to me and how much has changed, not just my life, but that of many people.

 “I try to look into people's hearts, because we know that's where we get the best from us.”

 Happy birthday Kim SeokJin.

text:
i am not supposed to write a long letter saying how much i love him but for sure m gonna do that as for now i dont have my phone to tweet, insta or watch any live if there is.. it feels empty soo i wanna say here despite the fact who reads it or not. DEAR JINIEEEE HAPPIEST BIRTHDAY LOVEEEE..
I AM THANKFUL TO YOU FOR YOUR PRESENCE, I AM THANKFUL TO YOU FOR ALL YOUR SMILES, LAUGHTER AND HAPPINESS, Enough to brighten up my day making me feel alive, helping me stay positive and calm when it's hard to. Thanks for all your hardwork and still showing us the happiest face despite the fact that you do get tired, you do suffer but still you gave us the best of us. I am no stupid to write such long thing for no reason but i can right it for you,  My only reason to smile, TO LIVE. life has been cruel to me but it will not matter unless i got to see your smiling face at the end of the day. Nahh no hardship matters unless i see you working hard and still laughing, spreading positivity. THANKS FOR BEING AN HEALING OINTMENT. THANKS FOR BEING ARMY'S SEOKJINIE, MY HAPPINESS, A SMILING WORLD OF MINE. THANKS FOR MAkING ME FALL IN LOVE WITH YOU, WITH MYSELF. i love you and the letters are supposed to end and my words they're not enough to tell how precious you're. LOVE YOU, AGAIN A VERY HAPPY BIRTHDAY.

Happy Birthday to our precious Worldwide hansome!!🥳

I don’t know where to start to tell you how much I love you and how much you fill my heart with good vibes every day since I’ve known you. Imagine all the good you’re giving to us through simple videos that mean everything to us. You are the rare and untraceable pearl in this world, you are a sun filled with beautiful rays that illuminate the heart of any Army! You’re so funny, beautiful, handsome, unique, and I love you so much for who you are, every girl would dream of having you by her sides. You bring me back the smile when I’m ok and when I’m not ok and I’ll be eternally grateful.
Your talent is one more reason that accentuated my love for you. Through your songs I see myself as in a mirror. You taught me to love and accept myself as I am, and it’s because of you that I am who I am today.

author: @GlitteredinDPR
text: im hours away from leaving to my own military training and i am going to miss you, Bangtan. you came into my life during Wings era, when i needed you the most and for that, you hold a very Special place in my heart. this will be my last chance to say these things and i wish i could be more thorough but, in short... MEGA HAPPY BIRTHDAY JIN, may your day be full of support and unforgettable memories! Jimin to have seen your vocals, fluid dance and mental health blossom, has been a beautiful gift. Kookie, you have grown into such a mesmerizing artist of heartbreak vocals and i couldn't be more proud; your cover of BIGBANG's "If You" is a timeless Gem. Hobi, my heart♡ you push yourself to your absolute Limits, all for your passion of dance and it is powerful. Jung Hoseok please know, i will never not be inspired by All that you are. Yoongi, your musical talents as a rapper, as a producer and sweetheart personality, you were meant for this life. i hope you continue to get the recognition. Tae, from growling your verses to stunning vocals, you are truly painted in your own color. just once, i'd like to see the world through your eyes. Joon you are a phenomenal leader and to see how your, already stellar, dance has improved. im grateful for how hard you work and everything you continue to do for the boys. which leads me back to you, Jin. i know you've cared for your brothers just as much. more than anything, the journey your vocals have taken is nothing short of moving and has genuinely brought me to tears, more than you can imagine. thank you all for your artistry, these past few years. for being my solace... thank you Bangtan, for being my Home. i love you, no. i purple you. Always♡

author: @devushkamin5147
text:
Знаете у кого сегодня День Рождения? А попробуйте угадать🙃) Этот человек необычайно красивый, восхитительный и покоряющий сердце с первого взгляда, с лёгкого, словно дуновение майского ветерка... 
По-моему легко догадаться, что это Всемирный Красавчик Ким Сокджин!!! 
Твои глаза ярче тысячи звёзд, прекраснее космоса. Сравнивать их с бездонным морем или ясным небом бесполезно, ведь они в миллионы раз лучше, уютнее, обворожительнее. Твой голос мягче хлопка или зефира, слаще конфетки и изящнее чего-либо на свете.
Но помимо этой завораживающей красоты ты ещё и прекрасный человек. Именно ты показываешь, что нужно заботиться о своих близких, что чаще необходимо показывать свою любовь, помогать во всём.
Ну и, конечно, самое приятное - поздравления!)
Во-первых желаю здоровья, ведь это очень важно, не хочу, чтобы Моя Любовь болел💜
Во-вторых счастья! 
В-третьих любви❤ Любви семьи, друзей, поклонников и, конечно, той самой, светлой, заставляющей сердце биться быстрее, а зрачки расширяться💜
И исполнения всех желаний, прекрасных (хотя куда лучше¿) друзей и всего самого наилучшего❤
Люблю безумно! Спасибо тебе за всё, за то что научил любить себя, научил меня заботиться о людях, ты мой лучик. Один из семи ударов моего сердца💜💜💜
